The [[Update Fiji|updater]] has a convenient ''Manage update sites'' dialog that is populated by this wiki page. You can add your own update site to this list by registering a wiki account and editing the table yourself (please maintain alphabetical order, but please do <b>not</b> change the format of the table: you will most likely break the [[Update Fiji|updater]] if you do).

Alternately, you may [[Help:Contents|send a message to the fiji-devel mailing list]] about it.
